WEBVTT

00:07:57.022 --> 00:08:00.816
that prevent their enormous stomach
from crushing their lungs.

00:08:01.258 --> 00:08:04.022
And their fur grows
the opposite direction,

00:08:04.046 --> 00:08:07.490
so they can drip dry
after a tropical drenching.

00:08:08.704 --> 00:08:13.667
The only problem is,
if you turn a sloth the other way up,

00:08:13.691 --> 00:08:16.783
gravity removes its dignity.

00:08:16.807 --> 00:08:18.017
Audience: Awww.

00:08:18.041 --> 00:08:20.839
They can't hold themselves upright.

00:08:20.863 --> 00:08:25.521
And so they drag their bodies along
as if mountaineering on a flat surface.

